foods.ingredients: INGREDIENTS: SKIM MILK, CREAM, SUGAR, CINNAMON CHURRO BASE (WATER, SUGAR, CORN STARCH, MOLASSES, CINNAMON POWDER, NATURAL FLAVORS), HONEY BUN SWIRL (POWDERED SUGAR, PEANUT OIL, NONFAT DRY MILK, WHEY POWDER, CINNAMON, SALT, NATURAL & ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, SOY LECITHIN, RED 40, YELLOW 6, BLUE 1), CORN SYRUP, CHURRO PIECES (CAKE MIX [SUGAR, BLEACHED ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR {WHEAT FLOUR, ENRICHED WITH NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID}, VEGETABLE SHORTENING {SOYBEAN OIL, VEGETABLE MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, PROPYLENE GLYCOL ESTER, SOY LECITHIN, TOCOPHEROLS (VITAMIN E), VITAMIN C PALMITATE (ANTIOXIDANTS)}, NONFAT DRY MILK, LEAVENING {SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE, BAKING SODA}, SALT, CORN STARCH-MODIFIED, DRIED WHOLE EGGS, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR], WATER, WHOLE EGG [WHOLE EGG, CITRIC ACID], SUGAR, NATURAL VANILLA FLAVOR, CINNAMON, SALT, NATURAL FLAVORS, NATURAL & ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, SOYBEAN OIL, POTASSIUM SORBATE [PRESERVATIVE]), WHEY, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF MONO- & DIGLYCERIDES, GUAR GUM, CALCIUM SULFATE, LOCUST BEAN GUM, CARRAGEENAN, DEXTROSE.
